date = "2019-05-03"
title = "Dynamic phases, split ergativity and adposition agreement in Avar"
host = "Cambridge Comparative Syntax 8: Comparative Perspectives on Phases "
publishdate = "2019-10-24"

+++

*Abstract*: In this talk, I develop a configurational approach to case and agreement in the Avar biabsolutive constructions.

This is a peer-reviewed talk, for the 8th installment of Cambridge Comparative Syntax at St John's College, Cambridge. 

You can view the slides [here](/papers/camcos8-slides.pdf)


